description: Income Restricted condo located in South Boston - Income Requirements 1 Household: Minimum $91,440 – Maximum $114,300. 2 Household: Minimum $104,480 – $130,600. Asset limit: $100,000 (does not include retirement). Discover a distinctive 1-bedroom unit spanning two levels within the Saints Peter & Paul Church Condominiums. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, a gas range, and backsplash. The separate bedroom downstairs comes complete with its own bathroom and convenient washer/dryer. The professionally managed building is pet-friendly and offers a common outdoor space. Enjoy the convenience of being steps away from the Broadway T station, granting easy access to a plethora of restaurants, grocery stores, the Seaport District, and downtown.
